org.antstudio.support.spring.annotation
注释类型 FormParam

@Target(value=PARAMETER)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Documented
public @interface FormParam

this annotation used for the @RequestMapping method, use like this: in the page there are parameters such as:user.id、user.userName、user.password and etc. in the hanlder method: public ModelAndView userValidate(@FormParam(value="user")User user){} then the user parameter would be made up with the parameter which name start with 'user.'
